{
  "stem": "6803.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember I was sitting there by the door like this here in the window, and I saw a man-- I knew the man.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a very learned man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to have sometimes conversation when he was still alive and was still healthy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was there and he was begging himself, let me in!",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were not allowed to open up the door for nobody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the way he said, let me in and then he's-- goes quiet and then how he died.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I thought to myself that time, if this man would take-- be taken into a house and given him a warm glass of tea and taken and put in a nice warm bath, he could be still alive and he could still contribute to the world.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I says, my god, this man should be just in a little-- in a home somewhere warmed up a little bit.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was hundreds of people like this here on the street in the camp scattered around.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were not allowed to open up the door.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is how they died-- naked, frozen, and outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, they were not even shooting them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, they were just-- this was--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she was in my home town, and she went with my aunt and uncle to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, she went on the-- on the left side with the children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES] She was only 14, When we were arrived in Ausch--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the same time, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister was, at that time, around 14.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't-- she-- she could have passed to go on the right side, but she wanted to go with the aunt.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
